, 
<figureCitation id="13462A3C335E5A485255A5C0493A32C2" box="[807,858,408,430]" captionStart-0="FIGURE 6" captionStart-1="FIGURE 7" captionStart-2="FIGURE 8" captionStart-3="FIGURE 9" captionStart-4="FIGURE 10" captionStart-5="FIGURE 11" captionStartId-0="6.[136,229,1953,1975]" captionStartId-1="7.[136,229,1898,1920]" captionStartId-2="8.[136,229,1931,1953]" captionStartId-3="9.[136,229,1125,1147]" captionStartId-4="10.[136,229,1953,1975]" captionStartId-5="11.[136,229,1054,1076]" captionTargetBox-0="[199,1388,190,1928]" captionTargetBox-1="[201,1386,190,1874]" captionTargetBox-2="[201,1386,190,1906]" captionTargetBox-3="[170,1417,190,1101]" captionTargetBox-4="[225,1363,281,1929]" captionTargetBox-5="[216,1371,190,1030]" captionTargetId-0="figure-18@6.[199,1388,190,1928]" captionTargetId-1="figure-20@7.[201,1386,190,1874]" captionTargetId-2="figure-18@8.[201,1386,190,1906]" captionTargetId-3="figure-20@9.[170,1417,190,1101]" captionTargetId-4="figure-57@10.[225,1363,281,1929]" captionTargetId-5="figure-20@11.[216,1371,190,1030]" captionTargetPageId-0="6" captionTargetPageId-1="7" captionTargetPageId-2="8" captionTargetPageId-3="9" captionTargetPageId-4="10" captionTargetPageId-5="11" captionText-0="FIGURE 6. Holotype and isotype sheets of Thalictrum tsawarungense.A. Holotype sheet (PE00028284) (inset a: flower; inset b: stamens; inset c: achene). B. Isotype sheet (GH00057586). C. Isotype sheet (NAS00070715). D. Isotype sheet (PE00028283)." captionText-1="FIGURE 7. Selected specimens of Thalictrum tsawarungense previously misidentified as T. rostellatum. A. China, Sichuan, Jinchuan, S. Jiang et al. 1078 (PE00450428) (inset: aggregate fruit). B. China, Sichuan, Kangding, Kangding-Dawu Exped. 247 (SM704604894) (inset: flower). C. China, Xizang, Bomi, Inst. Bio. Xizang Exped.376 (HNWP) (inset: aggregate fruit).D. China, Xizang, Lhunze, Qinghai- Xizang Exped. Suppl. Group 750543 (PE00450384) (inset: aggregate fruit)." captionText-2="FIGURE 8. Thalictrum chayuense (= T. tsawarungense) in the wild (China, Xizang, Zayu, the type locality). A. Habitat. B. Habit. C. Roots. D. Portion of stem. E. Leaf (left: adaxial side; right: abaxial side). F. Leaflet (adaxial side). G. Portion of adaxial side of leaflet. H. Portion of abaxial side of leaflet. I. Flower. J. Sepal (left: adaxial side; right: abaxial side). K. Stamens. L. Carpels. M. Aggregate fruits (immature). N. Achenes (immature). Photographed by Y.P. Zeng." captionText-3="FIGURE 9. Specimens of Thalictrum chayuense (= T. tsawarungense), Y.P. Zeng &amp; Q.L. Huang 565 (IBSC), from the type locality, i.e. Zayu in southeastern Xizang, China. Inset a: flower; inset b: aggregate fruit." captionText-4="FIGURE 10. Thalictrum tsawarungense in the wild (China, Xizang, Zayu county, Chawalong (= Tsawarung), the type locality). A. Habitat. B. Habit. C. Roots. D. Portion of stem. E. Leaf (left: adaxial side; right: abaxial side). F. Leaflet (adaxial side). G. Portion of adaxial side of leaflet. H. Portion of abaxial side of leaflet. I. Flower. J. Sepal (left: adaxial side; right: abaxial side). K. Stamens. L. Carpels. M.Aggregate fruits (immature). N. Achenes (immature). Photographed by Y.P. Zeng." captionText-5="FIGURE 11. Specimens of Thalictrum tsawarungense, Y.P. Zeng &amp; Q.L. Huang 540 (IBSC), from the type locality, i.e. Chawalong (= Tsawarung) in Zayu, southeastern Xizang, China.A. Inset: flower. B. Inset: aggregate fruit." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597767" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597769" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597773" figureDoi-3="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597775" figureDoi-4="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597777" figureDoi-5="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597779" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6597767/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6597769/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6597773/files/figure.png" httpUri-3="https://zenodo.org/record/6597775/files/figure.png" httpUri-4